summary: Rilasciato il nuovo logo ufficiale di Captain Marvel
title: Rilasciato il nuovo logo ufficiale di Captain Marvel
body:
Rilasciato il nuovo logo ufficiale di Captain Marvel

I Marvel Studios hanno svelato quest’oggi il nuovo logo ufficiale di Captain Marvel, il cinecomic diretto da Anna Boden e Ryan Fleck.

Il logo è in sostanza simile a quello precedente, l’unica differenza riguarda la luce “stellare” sullo sfondo. Che ne dite, meglio questo o il precedente?

Captain Marvel è diretto da Anna Boden e Ryan Fleck. La sceneggiatura è di Ginevra Robertson-Dworet e

summary: I have to rant about some Marvel things.
title: I have to rant about some Marvel things.
body:
1. Scarlett Johansson has signed a contract to be in a solo Black Widow movie.  😍

2. Avengers 4 will be Chris Evans’ last Marvel movie. 😭

3. The contract that Brie Larson has with Marvel is a seven movie deal! So it’s certain we will see her again as Captain Marvel!

summary: Okay, but imagine Captain Marvel bursting onto the scene with a huge grin on his face and announcing, "It's fine now! Why?...
body: Okay, but imagine Captain Marvel bursting onto the scene with a huge grin on his face and announcing, “It’s fine now! Why? Because I am here!” and people are freaking out because did Capt. Marvel really just reference BNHA? Captain Marvel watches anime?! And suddenly Billy’s one of the most popular superheroes on social media. He didn’t even realize it would blow up so much, he was just having fun. But yeah, I feel like he would really enjoy action anime/manga.

excerpt: Speed drawing of Luny cosplaying as Captain Marvel, the awesome Marvel comics character, and new adiction to the great Marvel/Disney MCU (Marvel Cinematic Un...
description:
How to draw CAPTAIN MARVEL (SPEED DRAWING I L&M Luny cosplay)

Speed drawing of Luny cosplaying as Captain Marvel, the awesome Marvel comics character, and new adiction to the great Marvel/Disney MCU (Marvel Cinematic Universe).
We really love the marvel universe, and this is one of the stronger characters today! So much so, that we had to pay this homage to it, with one of our main characters(Luny) cosplaying as Carol Danvers/Captain Marvel.

Enjoy the speed drawing/speedpaint, and the process on how it was flash illustrated.
And if you haven’t, check out the Captain Marvel comics, and keep an eye for the upcoming exciting MCU’s Captain Marvel movie :’)
